promoterAddress: Block No. 291,292,293,294 Angel Business Center-1, ABC Circle, Sudama Chowk, Mota Varachh, Surat. Surat 394101

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
TO THE BEST OF MY KNOWLEDGE IS TRUE AND FAIR. 
The promoter doesnt maintain Separate RERA Account however the management certifies the utilization of booking receipts towards project only. 
The promoter have not executed ATS of the customers and the dates given are dates of first payments.
The Details of Booked inventory also includes the name of the buyers in whose favour the Sale Document stands executed. Thus the Advance from Customers Ledger shall show a different value as the Value of Sales gets posted to other Ledger.
All the details are based on Unaudited Provisional Books of Accounts.
There is a difference of Rs. 111000 in the Amount received towards booked inventory between RERA Annexure 3A and actual receipts as per books of account since the amount received in unit named FF F139 is more than the estimated value mentioned in Annexure 3A by Rs. 100000.
The Promoter has  projects under this promoter firm and the Project ABC 1 enjoys an OD facility from State Bank of India. However, The OD facility is secured against the receivables of the the latter project ABC 1 as also against the receivables of this project concerned but no encumbrance has been reported in this project. 

We are informed by  the promoters that they have not obtained the physical copy of the BU Permission from the SMC however, reliance is placed o the Architect Completion Certificate and Application Made before the SMC for obtaining BU Permission. We do not express on any technical information provided in the Form 1 & Form 2 or Form 2A above. We express the opion based only on the Accounting Records of the firm. It may however by brought to the notice of RERA authorities from our end as a part of due diligence.
